# Supplier & Third-Party Cybersecurity Risk Management – Audit Checklist

## 1. Defined Risk Management Process
- [ ] Has the organization established a process to identify, assess, and prioritize the cybersecurity risks posed by its suppliers and other third-party service providers?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Dokumentierter Prozess für Supplier/Third-Party Risk Management
- Genehmigung durch Management / CISO
- Integration in ERM oder ISMS
- Historie der Prozessanpassungen

---

## 2. Evaluation Criteria & Methodologies
- [ ] What criteria and methodologies does the organization use to evaluate the cybersecurity risks associated with its suppliers and third parties (e.g., threat assessments, vulnerability scans, security control reviews)?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Bewertungsmethoden dokumentiert
- Einsatz von Threat Intelligence, Vulnerability Scans, Security Assessments
- Bewertungs-Kategorien (High/Medium/Low) klar definiert
- Nachweis der Anwendung in Praxisfällen

---

## 3. Centralized Inventory / Database
- [ ] How does the organization maintain a centralized inventory or database of the identified cybersecurity risks related to its suppliers and third-party relationships?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Supplier Risk Register oder Datenbank dokumentiert
- Zugriffskontrollen und Versionierung nachgewiesen
- Nachweis der Pflege und Aktualisierung
- Integration in Reporting / ERM

---

## 4. Integration into ERM & Risk Register
- [ ] Are the cybersecurity risks associated with suppliers and third parties integrated into the organization's overall enterprise risk management framework and risk register?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Mapping von Supplier-Risiken auf ERM-Risiken
- Nachweis in Risk Register oder Dashboard
- Management-Review-Dokumentation
- Konsistenzprüfung mit Unternehmensrichtlinien

---

## 5. Ongoing Monitoring & Updates
- [ ] What processes are in place to regularly monitor and update the cybersecurity risk profiles of the organization's suppliers and third-party service providers?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Regelmäßige Überprüfung dokumentiert (z. B. quartalsweise)
- Aktualisierung von Risiko-Bewertungen basierend auf Vorfällen oder Änderungen
- Nachweis von Management-Review oder Steering-Committee Meetings
- Tracking von Änderungen im Risk Register

---

## 6. Risk Response & Mitigation
- [ ] How does the organization respond to and mitigate the identified cybersecurity risks posed by its suppliers and third parties, based on the risk prioritization and assessment?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Risikobehandlungspläne dokumentiert
- Nachweis der Umsetzung von Maßnahmen
- Korrektur- und Eskalationsprozesse
- Integration in Business Continuity / Incident Response

---

## 7. Roles & Responsibilities
- [ ] Are there clear roles and responsibilities assigned for the ongoing management and monitoring of cybersecurity risks related to suppliers and third-party relationships?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- RACI-Matrix oder Governance-Dokumentation
- Benannte Teams / Personen für Supplier Risk Management
- Nachweis von Schulungen / Awareness
- Eskalations- und Freigabeprozesse dokumentiert

---

## 8. Guidance & Training
- [ ] Does the organization provide guidance or training to personnel responsible for supplier and third-party risk management activities?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Trainingsprogramme oder SOPs für beteiligte Teams
- Teilnahmeberichte und KPI Tracking
- Integration in Onboarding und kontinuierliche Schulungen
- Feedback-Mechanismen zur Verbesserung der Trainings

---

## 9. Leadership Oversight & Direction
- [ ] How does the organization's leadership oversee and provide direction on the management of cybersecurity risks associated with the supply chain and third-party relationships?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- Teilnahme von Führungskräften an Review-Meetings
- Offizielle Kommunikation von Richtlinien und Erwartungen
- Ressourcenbereitstellung für Umsetzung
- Nachweis der strategischen Einbindung in ERM

---

## 10. Measuring Effectiveness & Continuous Improvement
- [ ] Are there mechanisms in place to measure the effectiveness of the organization's supplier and third-party cybersecurity risk management processes and make improvements as needed?

**Audit Evidence / Prüfpunkte:**
- KPI/KRI Tracking für Supplier Risk Management
- Auditberichte oder externe Assessments
- Dokumentierte Lessons Learned oder Verbesserungsmaßnahmen
- Nachweis der Anpassung von Prozessen basierend auf Ergebnissen
